### 安全负例：创建动态表缺少 X-CSRF-TOKEN（应返回 403）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dynamic-tables
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$randomUUID}}

{
  "tableKey": "orders_csrf",
  "displayName": "订单-CSRF负例",
  "description": "CSRF 缺失校验",
  "dbType": "Sqlite",
  "fields": [
    {
      "name": "id",
      "displayName": "主键",
      "fieldType": "Long",
      "allowNull": false,
      "isPrimaryKey": true,
      "isAutoIncrement": true,
      "isUnique": true,
      "sortOrder": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 负例：schema/alter 更新不支持的结构属性（应返回 400）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dynamic-tables/orders/schema/alter
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$randomUUID}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "addFields": [],
  "updateFields": [
    {
      "name": "amount",
      "displayName": "金额（更新）",
      "length": 128
    }
  ],
  "removeFields": []
}

### 安全负例：记录写入缺少 Idempotency-Key（应返回 400）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dynamic-tables/orders/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "values": [
    { "field": "orderNo", "valueType": "String", "stringValue": "SO-NO-IDEMPOTENCY" },
    { "field": "amount", "valueType": "Decimal", "decimalValue": 109.99 }
  ]
}

### 安全负例：幂等冲突（同 key 不同 payload，第二次应返回 409）
@idemConflictDynamic = dynamic-record-conflict-001
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dynamic-tables/orders/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idemConflictDynamic}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "values": [
    { "field": "orderNo", "valueType": "String", "stringValue": "SO-CONFLICT-A" },
    { "field": "amount", "valueType": "Decimal", "decimalValue": 159.99 }
  ]
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dynamic-tables/orders/records
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idemConflictDynamic}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "values": [
    { "field": "orderNo", "valueType": "String", "stringValue": "SO-CONFLICT-B" },
    { "field": "amount", "valueType": "Decimal", "decimalValue": 188.88 }
  ]
}

